Quick formula to calculate how much you are up on a stock:

(Current price / price you bought at)

Take that number and subtract 1

Then multiply by 100

So if you bought $META at $88 (52 week low)

Today you are now up:

112/88 = 1.27

1.27 - 1 = .27

.27 (100) = 27%

In 3 days.
